dtk.el
================================

Read the Bible or other diatheke-accessible material in emacs. diatheke is a front-end to the SWORD library.


Use
--------------------------------

M-x dtk
     - read a portion of a text

M-x dtk-search
     - search the selected text

M-x dtk-select-module
     - select a module (e.g., KJV, ESV, or RNKJV)


Prerequisites
--------------------------------

dtk.el assumes diatheke is installed with the KJV


See also
--------------------------------

http://www.crosswire.org/wiki/Frontends:Diatheke

diatheke.el (http://www.jasonfruit.com/page/diatheke_el and https://github.com/JasonFruit/diatheke.el)
